#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:2
msgid "Secondary KV Storage"
msgstr "二级 KV 存储"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:4
msgid "LMCache multiprocess mode supports a two-tier storage architecture:"
msgstr "LMCache MP 模式（多进程）支持两级存储架构："

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:6
msgid ""
"**L1 (fast tier)** -- CPU memory by default, or an NVMe slab via "
"GPUDirect Storage (cuFile) when ``--gds-l1-path`` is set, managed by the "
"L1 Manager. All KV cache chunks live here during active use. (Byte-array "
"L2 adapters are unsupported under the GDS L1 tier, which exposes no L1 "
"memory buffer.)"
msgstr "**L1 (快速层)** -- 默认情况下为 CPU 内存，或通过 GPUDirect Storage (cuFile) 的 NVMe 块，当设置 ``--gds-l1-path`` 时，由 L1 管理器管理。所有 KV Cache 块在活跃使用期间都存放在这里。（在 GDS L1 层下，不支持字节数组 L2 适配器，因为它不暴露任何 L1 内存缓冲区。）"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:10
msgid ""
"**L2 (persistent)** -- Durable storage backends (NIXL-based or plain "
"file-system/raw-block).  The StoreController asynchronously pushes data "
"from L1 to L2, and the PrefetchController loads data from L2 back into L1"
" on cache misses."
msgstr "**L2 (持久性)** -- 持久存储后端（基于 NIXL 或普通文件系统/原始块）。StoreController 异步将数据从 L1 推送到 L2，而 PrefetchController 在缓存未命中时将数据从 L2 加载回 L1。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:20
msgid "Data Flow"
msgstr "数据流"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:22
msgid "**Write path (L1 -> L2):**"
msgstr "**写入路径 (L1 -> L2):**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:24
msgid "vLLM stores KV cache chunks into L1 via the ``STORE`` RPC."
msgstr "vLLM 通过 ``STORE`` RPC 将 KV Cache 块存储到 L1。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:25
msgid ""
"The ``StoreController`` detects new objects (via eventfd) and "
"asynchronously submits store tasks to each configured L2 adapter."
msgstr "``StoreController`` 通过 eventfd 检测新对象，并异步将存储任务提交到每个已配置的 L2 适配器。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:27
msgid "The L2 adapter writes the data to its backend (e.g., local SSD via GDS)."
msgstr "L2 适配器将数据写入其后端（例如，通过 GDS 的本地 SSD）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:29
msgid "**Read path (L2 -> L1):**"
msgstr "**读取路径 (L2 -> L1):**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:31
msgid "A ``LOOKUP`` RPC checks L1 for prefix hits."
msgstr "``LOOKUP`` RPC 检查 L1 中的前缀缓存命中情况。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:32
msgid ""
"For keys not found in L1, the ``PrefetchController`` submits lookup "
"requests to L2 adapters."
msgstr "对于在 L1 中未找到的键，\\ ``PrefetchController`` 向 L2 适配器提交查找请求。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:34
msgid ""
"If found in L2, the data is loaded back into L1 and read-locked for the "
"pending ``RETRIEVE`` RPC."
msgstr "如果在 L2 中找到，数据将被加载回 L1，并为待处理的 ``RETRIEVE`` RPC 加读锁。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:38
msgid "Adapter Types"
msgstr "适配器类型"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:40
msgid ""
"LMCache ships several L2 storage backends, grouped by medium under "
":doc:`Supported Backends <supported_storages>`. Select one or more with "
"the ``--l2-adapter`` flag."
msgstr "LMCache 提供了几种 L2 存储后端，按介质分组在 :doc:`支持的后端 <supported_storages>` 下。使用 ``--l2-adapter`` 标志选择一个或多个。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:50
msgid "Multiple Adapters (Cascade)"
msgstr "多个适配器（级联）"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:52
msgid ""
"You can configure multiple L2 adapters by repeating the ``--l2-adapter`` "
"argument.  Adapters are used in the order they are specified.  The "
"``StoreController`` pushes data to all configured adapters, and the "
"``PrefetchController`` queries adapters in order during lookups."
msgstr "您可以通过重复 ``--l2-adapter`` 参数来配置多个 L2 适配器。适配器按指定的顺序使用。\\ ``StoreController`` 将数据推送到所有配置的适配器，而 ``PrefetchController`` 在查找期间按顺序查询适配器。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:64
msgid "Store and Prefetch Policies"
msgstr "存储和预取策略"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:66
msgid ""
"The **store policy** controls how keys flow from L1 to L2: which adapters"
" receive each key and whether keys are deleted from L1 after a successful"
" L2 store.  The **prefetch policy** controls how keys flow from L2 back "
"to L1: when multiple adapters have the same key, the policy decides which"
" adapter loads it."
msgstr "**存储策略** 控制键从 L1 流向 L2 的方式：哪些适配器接收每个键，以及在成功存储到 L2 后是否从 L1 删除键。 **预取策略** 控制键从 L2 流回 L1 的方式：当多个适配器具有相同的键时，策略决定哪个适配器加载它。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:72
msgid "Select policies via CLI:"
msgstr "通过 CLI 选择策略："

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:79
msgid "**Built-in policies:**"
msgstr "**内置策略：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:85
#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:118
#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:177
msgid "Flag"
msgstr "标志"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:86
msgid "Name"
msgstr "名称"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:87
msgid "Behaviour"
msgstr "行为"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:88
#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:91
msgid "``--l2-store-policy``"
msgstr "``--l2-store-policy``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:89
#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:97
msgid "``default``"
msgstr "``default``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:90
msgid "Store all keys to all adapters.  Never delete from L1."
msgstr "将所有键存储到所有适配器中。永不从 L1 中删除。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:92
msgid "``skip_l1``"
msgstr "``skip_l1``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:93
msgid ""
"Buffer-only mode.  Store all keys to all adapters, then **delete them "
"from L1** immediately.  Pair with ``--eviction-policy noop`` to avoid "
"useless LRU overhead."
msgstr "仅缓冲区模式。将所有键存储到所有适配器，然后立即 **从 L1 中删除它们**\\ 。与 ``--eviction-policy noop`` 配对以避免无用的 LRU 开销。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:96
#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:100
msgid "``--l2-prefetch-policy``"
msgstr "``--l2-prefetch-policy``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:98
msgid ""
"For each key, pick the first (lowest-indexed) adapter that has it. "
"Prefetched keys are **temporary** (deleted after the reader finishes)."
msgstr "对于每个键，选择第一个（索引最低的）拥有该键的适配器。预取的键是\\ **临时的**\\ （在读取完成后删除）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:101
msgid "``retain``"
msgstr "``retain``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:102
msgid ""
"Same load plan as ``default``, but prefetched keys are **retained** "
"permanently in L1.  Useful when prefetched data is likely reused by "
"subsequent requests (e.g. shared system-prompt chunks)."
msgstr "与 ``default`` 相同的加载计划，但预取的键将\\ **永久保留**\\ 在 L1 中。当预取的数据可能被后续请求重用时（例如，共享系统提示块），此策略非常有用。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:107
msgid "Prefetch Concurrency"
msgstr "预取并发性"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:109
msgid ""
"The ``--l2-prefetch-max-in-flight`` flag limits the number of concurrent "
"prefetch requests that the ``PrefetchController`` can have in flight at "
"any time.  A higher value increases L2-to-L1 throughput but also "
"increases L1 memory pressure from in-flight data."
msgstr "``--l2-prefetch-max-in-flight`` 标志限制了 ``PrefetchController`` 在任意时刻可以并发进行的预取请求数量。较大的值会提升 L2 到 L1 的吞吐量，但也会增加在途数据对 L1 内存的压力。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:119
#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:178
#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:218
msgid "Default"
msgstr "默认"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:120
#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:179
#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:219
msgid "Description"
msgstr "描述"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:121
msgid "``--l2-prefetch-max-in-flight``"
msgstr "``--l2-prefetch-max-in-flight``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:122
msgid "``8``"
msgstr "``8``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:123
msgid "Maximum number of concurrent prefetch requests."
msgstr "最大并发预取请求数。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:126
msgid "Buffer-Only Mode"
msgstr "仅缓冲区模式"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:128
msgid ""
"When L1 is used purely as a write buffer (all data lives in L2), use "
"``--l2-store-policy skip_l1`` together with ``--eviction-policy noop``. "
"This combination deletes keys from L1 as soon as they are stored to L2 "
"and disables the LRU eviction tracker entirely, reducing memory and CPU "
"overhead."
msgstr "当 L1 仅作为写缓冲区使用（所有数据存储在 L2 中）时，使用 ``--l2-store-policy skip_l1`` 以及 ``--eviction-policy noop``\\ 。此组合会在数据存储到 L2 后立即从 L1 中删除键，并完全禁用 LRU 逐出跟踪器，从而减少内存和 CPU 开销。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:140
msgid ""
"Policies are extensible -- new policies can be added by creating a file "
"in ``storage_controllers/`` and calling ``register_store_policy()`` or "
"``register_prefetch_policy()`` at import time.  See the design doc "
"``l2_adapters/design_docs/overall.md`` for details."
msgstr "策略是可扩展的——可以通过在 ``storage_controllers/`` 中创建文件并在导入时调用 ``register_store_policy()`` 或 ``register_prefetch_policy()`` 来添加新策略。有关详细信息，请参阅设计文档 ``l2_adapters/design_docs/overall.md``\\ 。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:146
msgid "Serde (compression / quantization)"
msgstr "序列化与反序列化（压缩 / 量化）"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:148
msgid ""
"Each adapter can optionally run a **serde** (serializer / deserializer) "
"that transforms data on the way in and out of L2 — e.g. fp8 quantization "
"for disk backends, or encryption for remote adapters. See :doc:`KV Cache "
"Compression </mp/serde>` for details and configuration."
msgstr "每个适配器可以选择性地运行一个 **serde**\\ （序列化器/反序列化器），在数据进出 L2 时进行转换——例如，针对磁盘后端的 fp8 量化，或针对远程适配器的加密。有关详细信息和配置，请参见 :doc:`KV Cache Compression </mp/serde>`。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:159
msgid "Eviction"
msgstr "逐出"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:161
msgid ""
"LMCache supports eviction at both storage tiers so that each tier can "
"operate within a fixed capacity budget."
msgstr "LMCache 支持在两个存储层次上进行逐出，以便每个层次都可以在固定的容量预算内运行。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:165
msgid "L1 Eviction"
msgstr "L1 逐出"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:167
msgid ""
"L1 eviction runs a single background thread that monitors overall L1 "
"memory usage. When usage exceeds ``trigger_watermark``, the eviction "
"policy evicts a fraction of the least-recently-used keys."
msgstr "L1 逐出运行一个后台线程，监控整体 L1 内存使用情况。当使用量超过 ``trigger_watermark`` 时，逐出策略会逐出一部分最近最少使用的键。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:171
msgid "**CLI flags:**"
msgstr "**命令行标志:**"

