#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:190
msgid "**Example:**"
msgstr "**示例：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:199
msgid "L2 Eviction"
msgstr "L2 逐出"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:201
msgid ""
"L2 eviction is **per-adapter** and **opt-in**. Each adapter can "
"independently declare an eviction policy by adding an ``\"eviction\"`` "
"sub-object to its ``--l2-adapter`` JSON spec. Adapters without an "
"``\"eviction\"`` key have no eviction controller."
msgstr "L2 逐出是\\ **按适配器独立配置**\\ 且\\ **可选启用**\\ 的。每个适配器可以通过在其 ``--l2-adapter`` JSON 规范中添加 ``\"eviction\"`` 子对象来独立声明逐出策略。没有 ``\"eviction\"`` 键的适配器不启用逐出控制器。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:206
msgid ""
"When L2 eviction is enabled for an adapter, a dedicated background thread"
" monitors that adapter's ``get_usage()`` value. Once usage exceeds "
"``trigger_watermark``, the policy evicts keys until usage drops by "
"``eviction_ratio``."
msgstr "当为适配器启用 L2 逐出时，一个专用的后台线程会监控该适配器的 ``get_usage()`` 值。一旦使用量超过 ``trigger_watermark``\\ ，该策略将逐出键，直到使用量降低 ``eviction_ratio``\\ 。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:211
msgid "**``\"eviction\"`` sub-object fields:**"
msgstr "**``\"eviction\"`` 子对象字段:**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:217
msgid "Field"
msgstr "字段"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:220
msgid "``eviction_policy``"
msgstr "``eviction_policy``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:222
msgid "Policy name: ``\"LRU\"`` or ``\"noop\"``."
msgstr "策略名称：\\ ``\"LRU\"`` 或 ``\"noop\"``\\ 。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:223
msgid "``trigger_watermark``"
msgstr "``trigger_watermark``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:225
msgid "Adapter usage fraction [0, 1] above which eviction is triggered."
msgstr "触发逐出的适配器使用比例 [0, 1]。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:226
msgid "``eviction_ratio``"
msgstr "``eviction_ratio``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:228
msgid "Fraction of used capacity to evict per cycle."
msgstr "每个周期逐出的已用容量的比例。"

