msgid "**Example — nixl_store with LRU eviction:**"
msgstr "**示例 — 使用 LRU 逐出的 nixl_store:**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:246
msgid "**Adapter support:**"
msgstr "**适配器支持：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:252
msgid "Adapter"
msgstr "适配器"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:253
msgid "L2 Eviction Support"
msgstr "L2 逐出支持"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:254
msgid "``nixl_store``"
msgstr "``nixl_store``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:255
msgid ""
"Full support. ``delete`` frees pool slots; pinned keys (in-flight loads) "
"are skipped and retried on the next cycle."
msgstr "完全支持。\\ ``delete`` 释放池槽；固定的键（正在进行的加载）会被跳过，并在下一个周期重试。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:257
msgid "``nixl_store_dynamic``"
msgstr "``nixl_store_dynamic``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:258
msgid ""
"Full support. ``delete`` removes data files from disk; pinned keys are "
"skipped. ``get_usage`` is byte-based (``_total_bytes / "
"max_capacity_bytes``)."
msgstr "完全支持。\\ ``delete`` 从磁盘中删除数据文件；被固定的键会被跳过。\\ ``get_usage`` 是基于字节的 (``_total_bytes / max_capacity_bytes``)。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:261
msgid "``mock``"
msgstr "``mock``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:262
msgid ""
"Full support. Useful for testing eviction behaviour without real storage "
"hardware."
msgstr "完全支持。适用于在无真实存储硬件的情况下测试逐出行为。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:264
msgid "``raw_block``"
msgstr "``raw_block``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:265
msgid ""
"Full shared/global eviction support. ``delete`` recycles raw-block slots;"
" locked entries are skipped and retried on the next cycle."
msgstr "完全支持共享/全局逐出。\\ ``delete`` 回收原始块槽；被锁定的条目会被跳过，并在下一个周期重试。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:267
msgid "``s3``"
msgstr "``s3``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:268
msgid ""
"``delete`` removes objects from the bucket and frees aggregate byte "
"accounting. ``get_usage`` reports ``usage_fraction == -1.0`` when "
"``max_capacity_gb`` is ``0`` (disabled); set a non-zero "
"``max_capacity_gb`` to enable the watermark-triggered eviction "
"controller."
msgstr "``delete`` 从存储桶中移除对象并释放聚合字节计数。当 ``max_capacity_gb`` 为 ``0``\\ （禁用）时，\\ ``get_usage`` 报告 ``usage_fraction == -1.0``\\ ；设置非零的 ``max_capacity_gb`` 以启用基于水印的逐出控制器。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:273
msgid "``hfbucket``"
msgstr "``hfbucket``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:274
msgid ""
"``delete`` removes objects from the bucket and frees aggregate byte "
"accounting. ``get_usage`` reports ``usage_fraction == -1.0`` when "
"``max_capacity_gb`` is ``0`` (disabled); set a non-zero "
"``max_capacity_gb`` to enable the watermark-triggered eviction "
"controller. Locked keys (in-flight loads) are skipped."
msgstr "``delete`` 从桶中移除对象并释放聚合字节计数。当 ``max_capacity_gb`` 为 ``0``\\ （禁用）时，\\ ``get_usage`` 报告 ``usage_fraction == -1.0``\\ ；设置非零的 ``max_capacity_gb`` 以启用基于水印的逐出控制器。锁定的键（正在加载的）会被跳过。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:279
msgid "``dax``"
msgstr "``dax``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:280
msgid ""
"Full support. ``delete`` removes unlocked keys from the in-memory index "
"immediately and recycles fixed slots once active read borrows drain. "
"Usage is slot-based."
msgstr "完全支持。\\ ``delete`` 会立即从内存索引中移除未锁定的键，并在活跃读取借用排空后回收固定槽。使用量以槽数为单位计算。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:283
msgid "``mooncake_store``"
msgstr "``mooncake_store``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:284
msgid "No eviction support (native connector adapter)."
msgstr "不支持逐出（原生连接器适配器）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:285
msgid "``fs``"
msgstr "``fs``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:286
msgid "No eviction support (``delete`` and ``get_usage`` are no-ops)."
msgstr "不支持逐出（\\ ``delete`` 和 ``get_usage`` 均为空操作）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:287
msgid "native connectors"
msgstr "原生连接器"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:288
msgid "No eviction support."
msgstr "不支持逐出。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/index.rst:292
msgid ""
"Each L2 adapter instance gets its own independent eviction controller and"
" policy.  Two adapters of the same type can have different watermarks or "
"policies."
msgstr "每个 L2 适配器实例都有自己独立的逐出控制器和策略。两个相同类型的适配器可以有不同的水位线或策略。"

